%%{init: {
  'theme': 'base',
  'themeVariables': {
    'primaryColor': '#087EA4',
    'primaryTextColor': '#FFFFFF',
    'primaryBorderColor': '#044E68',
    'secondaryColor': '#E6F7FF',
    'secondaryTextColor': '#23272F',
    'secondaryBorderColor': '#149ECA',
    'tertiaryColor': '#F6F7F9',
    'tertiaryTextColor': '#23272F',
    'lineColor': '#99A1B3',
    'textColor': '#23272F',
    'fontSize': '13px',
    'fontFamily': '"PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif'
  },
  'flowchart': {
    'nodeSpacing': 30,
    'rankSpacing': 50,
    'padding': 15,
    'wrappingWidth': 120
  }
}}%%
flowchart TB
    classDef primary fill:#087EA4,stroke:#044E68,color:#FFFFFF,stroke-width:2px,rx:12,ry:12
    classDef secondary fill:#E6F7FF,stroke:#149ECA,color:#23272F,stroke-width:1.5px,rx:8,ry:8
    classDef accent fill:#149ECA,stroke:#087EA4,color:#FFFFFF,stroke-width:2px,rx:8,ry:8
    classDef result fill:#044E68,stroke:#023347,color:#FFFFFF,stroke-width:2px,rx:12,ry:12

    Start([URL 请求]):::primary
    Net[网络请求]:::secondary
    Resp[接收响应]:::secondary

    Start --> Net --> Resp

    HTML[解析 HTML]:::accent
    DOM[构建 DOM 树]:::secondary
    CSS[解析 CSS]:::accent
    CSSOM[构建 CSSOM 树]:::secondary
    JS[执行 JS]:::accent

    Resp --> HTML
    Resp --> CSS
    HTML --> DOM
    CSS --> CSSOM
    JS -.->|操作| DOM
    JS -.->|修改| CSSOM
    Resp --> JS

    RT[合并渲染树]:::accent
    Layout[布局计算]:::secondary
    Paint[绘制图层]:::secondary
    Composite[合成显示]:::secondary
    Display([页面呈现]):::result

    DOM --> RT
    CSSOM --> RT
    RT --> Layout --> Paint --> Composite --> Display

    style Start stroke-width:2.5px
    style Display stroke-width:2.5px
